<lb ed="I" n="0251b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0251b0101">左葙都維那王仕力金<note n="0251001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31110"/>＝剛【史】</note><note n="0251001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31110"/>【佛拓】，剛【史】</note><app n="0251001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31110"/></rdg></app>主王始
